                    <span>Often when in such a class, European immigrants are not thought of as having as much of a struggle. This book about an East. European family is very heart-wrenching and interesting.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">This is a good book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
